== 發行 ==
電影在2015年5月1日首次正式公映。<ref>{{cite web|last=Thompson|first=Anne|title=Far from the Madding Crowd' To Open from Fox Searchlight Next May|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/far-from-the-madding-crowd-to-open-from-fox-searchlight-next-may-video|work=Thompson on Hollywood|access-date=2017-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019030101/http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/far-from-the-madding-crowd-to-open-from-fox-searchlight-next-may-video|archive-date=2014-10-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2015/apr/24/far-from-the-madding-crowd-hardys-novel|first = Lucasta|last=Miller|title= Far from the Madding Crowd, Does the film live up to Hardy's Novel|publisher =[[The_Guardian|Guardian]] Review Section|date = 25 April 2015|accessdate = 3 May 2015}}</ref>第一支預告片花於2014年11月23日釋出，片花中使用了由[[凱莉·墨里根|凱莉·墨里根]]和[[麥可·辛|麥可·辛]]演唱的英國民謠《{{tsl|en|The Sprig of Thyme|The Sprig of Thyme}}》。此外，還發佈了一款前導海報以紀念同名小說問世140週年。<ref>{{cite web|title=Far From the Madding Crowd: watch the teaser trailer|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/culturevideo/filmvideo/cinema-trailers/11245788/Far-From-the-Madding-Crowd-watch-the-first-trailer.html|accessdate=23 November 2014 |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|Telegraph]]}}</ref>

